{"id": "1506644693113503844", "channel_id": "1506644693113503844", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "⚠️Ship: Goliath×Caecus⚠️\nCan you walk on the water if I, you and I\nBecause your blood's running cold outside the familiar true to life\nCan you walk on the water if I, you and I\nOr keep your eyes on the road and live the familiar without you and I\n——Agnes Obel《Familiär》\n​Private Commission | All Rights Reserved\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T13:08:06.943000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506644693331476501", "filename": "Image_1779248249907.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 894536, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506644693113503844/1506644693331476501/Image_1779248249907.png?ex=6a0f03b6&is=6a0db236&hm=85aa65ed1bf380c285632ae26704f7bc8b2f8359b117bc2c35500266e02fd60f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506644693113503844", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[Goliath Birthday Project 2026] Familiär", "forum_channel_id": "1304022107847659520", "thread_tags": ["1441261233461264476"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1506628341124567081", "channel_id": "1506628341124567081", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "⚠️Ship: Goliath×Caecus⚠️\nI want to be free\nI want to to be free without my pain\nI want to see dreams\nSea of dreams\nPlease stand by me\n——Rauf&Faik《ДОМ》\n​Private Commission | All Rights Reserved\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T12:03:08.325000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "goliath_spend", "emoji_id": "1468259820875415728", "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506628341841662086", "filename": "Image_1779248243024.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1571383, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506628341124567081/1506628341841662086/Image_1779248243024.png?ex=6a0ef47c&is=6a0da2fc&hm=fd7c933261dd5c5b90837b81e08f83061d9f48ad2ee7adfaeb61f7e942edf068&"}, {"id": "1506628342621667338", "filename": "Image_1779248243703.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1672401, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506628341124567081/1506628342621667338/Image_1779248243703.png?ex=6a0ef47c&is=6a0da2fc&hm=1eccea1679cdf0ce91d77c485c0d021c63b069b7443a10338422cc7a8541f307&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506628341124567081", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[Goliath Birthday Project 2026] ДОМ", "forum_channel_id": "1304022107847659520", "thread_tags": ["1441261233461264476"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1506619693358780428", "channel_id": "1506619693358780428", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "Lady, running down to the riptide\nTaken away to the dark side\nI wanna be your left hand man\nI love you when you're singing that song and\nI got a lump in my throat because\nYou're gonna sing the words wrong\n——Vancouver Sleep Clinic/ Pop Goes Ambient《Riptide》\n​Private Commission | All Rights Reserved\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T11:28:46.537000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Caecus_prayer", "emoji_id": "1459077248089853962", "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506619694138916954", "filename": "Image_1779248870575.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 803511, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506619693358780428/1506619694138916954/Image_1779248870575.png?ex=6a0eec6e&is=6a0d9aee&hm=3ee64e6103b87b895d5a9150110f3317af1f296b9bff5bcee22e6980c2d3baa1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506619693358780428", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[Goliath Birthday Project 2026] Riptide", "forum_channel_id": "1304022107847659520", "thread_tags": ["1441261233461264476"], "is_thread_starter": true}
